1
00:01:55,439 --> 00:01:58,079
I'm with Xiaowei. Is that shameful?

2
00:01:59,040 --> 00:02:01,640
I live my own life. Is that shameful?

3
00:02:02,140 --> 00:02:05,219
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant. Is that shameful?

4
00:02:05,219 --> 00:02:06,099
Is it shameful?

5
00:02:07,920 --> 00:02:10,080
If I can have this baby, I can raise it.

6
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:12,659
I own my choices.

7
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:14,599
Is it shameful?

8
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:19,199
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant. Is that shameful?

9
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:20,300
Is it shameful?

10
00:02:22,020 --> 00:02:24,099
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant.

11
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,740
It's not shameful.

12
00:02:27,139 --> 00:02:28,560
It's not shameful.

13
00:02:43,060 --> 00:02:44,080
Uncle.

14
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:45,800
Why didn't you go after Xiaowei?

15
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,259
I'm a scholar.

16
00:02:48,740 --> 00:02:49,680
They're the warriors.

17
00:02:50,360 --> 00:02:51,000
I've got my dignity.

18
00:02:52,780 --> 00:02:54,240
Are you afraid you can't beat Xiaowei?

19
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,539
I've been training.

20
00:02:55,539 --> 00:02:56,400
Me? Afraid of him?

21
00:02:58,639 --> 00:02:59,219
Listen, let me tell you.

22
00:02:59,219 --> 00:02:59,759
Once I get home,

23
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:00,740
I'm definitely gonna get attacked.

24
00:03:00,860 --> 00:03:01,759
You've gotta protect me.

25
00:03:01,819 --> 00:03:03,900
Don't worry. Leave it to me. I've got you.

26
00:03:19,580 --> 00:03:19,960
Brother.

27
00:03:20,780 --> 00:03:22,300
Your house still isn't fixed up.

28
00:03:22,539 --> 00:03:22,939
The roof.

29
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,680
I've fixed it a few times.

30
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,099
Still not quite right, huh?

31
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:28,599
Alright.

32
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:29,620
In a couple of days,

33
00:03:30,300 --> 00:03:31,740
I'll fix it up again.

34
00:03:32,060 --> 00:03:33,419
Every problem in this world

35
00:03:33,419 --> 00:03:34,680
is a leftover from the past.

36
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,379
By the time you spot the anthill,

37
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,319
the dam's already about to burst.

38
00:03:39,219 --> 00:03:39,780
Right.

39
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,500
By the time you see the big belly,

40
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,780
that baby's about to burst out too.

41
00:03:45,180 --> 00:03:45,960
What are you saying?

42
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:53,860
Smells amazing.

43
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:57,000
You guys...

44
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,259
You've all been so busy.

45
00:03:59,259 --> 00:03:59,719
Give it here, give it here.

46
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,099
Over this whole thing,

47
00:04:01,159 --> 00:04:02,080
I had to call you all back.

48
00:04:03,099 --> 00:04:03,879
I feel bad about it.

49
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:04,300
Brother.

50
00:04:04,699 --> 00:04:05,659
What are you talking about?

51
00:04:06,139 --> 00:04:06,659
What could be

52
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:08,539
more important than family?

53
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:10,740
Exactly.

54
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,379
I've got plenty of free time anyway.

55
00:04:12,620 --> 00:04:13,539
I don't have anything going on.

56
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:16,680
You all love red kidney beans, right?

57
00:04:17,819 --> 00:04:19,660
I'll add extra for you today.

58
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,680
Thanks, brother.

59
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:23,160
Today,

60
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,680
I'll make everyone

61
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:25,720
crispy pork bits

62
00:04:26,180 --> 00:04:27,079
with diced potatoes.

63
00:04:28,379 --> 00:04:29,319
Xiaofang's favorite, right?

64
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:31,319
Thanks, Auntie.

65
00:04:32,839 --> 00:04:33,800
Sis, stir-fry some cured pork for me.

66
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,600
Your face looks like cured pork.

67
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:37,000
Drool over it and starve.

68
00:05:11,139 --> 00:05:11,939
Old man

69
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:13,660
This year,

70
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,259
thanks to our granddaughter,

71
00:05:16,019 --> 00:05:16,740
even with you,

72
00:05:16,939 --> 00:05:18,660
all seven of us

73
00:05:18,759 --> 00:05:20,300
are finally together.

74
00:05:21,199 --> 00:05:21,779
Grandma,

75
00:05:22,519 --> 00:05:23,360
eight of us.

76
00:05:23,920 --> 00:05:24,420
Right, right, right.

77
00:05:24,699 --> 00:05:25,300
Eight of us.

78
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,139
Four generations under one roof.

79
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,399
Mom,

80
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,439
you just keep spoiling her.

81
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:30,959
Here we go, here we go.

82
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:31,540
Plenty to go around.

83
00:05:31,540 --> 00:05:34,160
Now this is a real family reunion!

84
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:34,579
Mom.

85
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:36,899
Fanyan,

86
00:05:37,459 --> 00:05:39,040
this year's Mid-Autumn Festival,

87
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:41,139
you make sure to do it right.

88
00:05:42,019 --> 00:05:42,480
Don't worry.

89
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:45,019
I'll definitely win back the face

90
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:45,860
we lost in the village.

91
00:05:45,899 --> 00:05:46,459
That's enough, enough.

92
00:05:57,740 --> 00:05:58,060
Here.

93
00:05:59,300 --> 00:05:59,920
You all eat up.

94
00:06:08,540 --> 00:06:09,019
Big sis,

95
00:06:10,220 --> 00:06:11,240
weren't you going to the Maldives?

96
00:06:15,019 --> 00:06:15,779
Could I even go?

97
00:06:19,579 --> 00:06:21,220
Could I even go?

98
00:06:24,319 --> 00:06:26,860
I didn't stop you, Auntie.

99
00:06:30,379 --> 00:06:31,639
Sis, your husband and Dandan,

100
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,420
didn't come back with you?

101
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,060
This is so spicy.

102
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:39,740
Eat slowly.

103
00:06:43,860 --> 00:06:44,699
That's not important.

104
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:45,680
This time we came

105
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,379
to talk about Xiaofang, right?

106
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,060
Xiaofang.

107
00:06:59,019 --> 00:07:00,480
How can you act like nothing happened?

108
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:02,240
Because nothing's wrong with me.

109
00:07:02,699 --> 00:07:03,939
You call this nothing?

110
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:05,699
The whole family

111
00:07:05,939 --> 00:07:07,180
is worried sick over you.

112
00:07:07,220 --> 00:07:08,500
How can you be so heartless?

113
00:07:08,699 --> 00:07:10,019
The baby's inside me,

114
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,480
and Qi Xiaowei's right there.

115
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:13,259
Do you have to act like the sky's falling?

116
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,019
Let's just eat. Smells great.

117
00:07:15,019 --> 00:07:15,879
Xiaofang.

118
00:07:16,379 --> 00:07:17,259
The Qi family

119
00:07:17,579 --> 00:07:19,480
practically went back on their word today.

120
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:20,699
If they refuse to own up,

121
00:07:21,139 --> 00:07:22,079
what are you gonna do?

122
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,019
Today, up on the mountain...

123
00:07:24,439 --> 00:07:25,720
I, Yang Xiaofang, am pregnant.

124
00:07:25,860 --> 00:07:26,779
Is that shameful?

125
00:07:27,699 --> 00:07:28,800
You tell me, is it?

126
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,420
I think

127
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,199
it's not shameful.

128
00:07:36,139 --> 00:07:37,839
Stop with your "I think, I think."

129
00:07:38,339 --> 00:07:39,339
What you think doesn't matter.

130
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,639
It's what others think.

131
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:41,959
Everyone else thinks

132
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,100
you're loose.

133
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,420
What matters is how they see you.

134
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,180
Your lipstick's smudged.

135
00:07:47,420 --> 00:07:47,939
Wipe it off.

136
00:07:49,079 --> 00:07:50,860
I'm not even wearing lipstick!

137
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,839
Fine, I won't say anything. Happy?

138
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,519
I shouldn't have come back at all.

139
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,079
Meddling in all your mess.

140
00:08:01,459 --> 00:08:02,959
You came back to see your mom.

141
00:08:03,899 --> 00:08:05,060
Was that pointless or not?

142
00:08:06,699 --> 00:08:08,160
No, no, it wasn't.

143
00:08:11,180 --> 00:08:11,959
From now on,

144
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:14,959
don't ruin the mood at the table.

145
00:08:15,759 --> 00:08:17,040
Same rule as always.

146
00:08:17,740 --> 00:08:19,339
If you've got something to argue about,

147
00:08:19,959 --> 00:08:21,800
argue after we've eaten.

148
00:08:21,959 --> 00:08:25,139
Nothing's more important than eating.

149
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:25,800
Come on.

150
00:08:26,339 --> 00:08:27,019
Mom's right.

151
00:08:27,019 --> 00:08:28,579
It's not easy for us all to get together.

152
00:08:28,579 --> 00:08:29,100
Right?

153
00:08:29,139 --> 00:08:30,220
Thanks for your hard work. Cheers.

154
00:08:30,220 --> 00:08:30,839
Thanks, thanks, brother.

155
00:08:30,839 --> 00:08:31,480
Thanks for your hard work, brother.

156
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:31,939
Thanks, brother.

157
00:08:32,500 --> 00:08:33,759
I also chilled a watermelon.

158
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:34,799
Let me go get it.

159
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:37,080
Xiaofang.

160
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:40,059
These are the tofu balls you love.

161
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,519
Your dad bought them first thing this morning.

162
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:45,820
Nice, really cold.

163
00:08:46,259 --> 00:08:47,480
It's all cracked open.

164
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,600
Come on, come on, dig in.

165
00:08:49,379 --> 00:08:50,600
Eat, eat, eat.

166
00:08:53,179 --> 00:08:54,039
Time to eat.

167
00:08:58,200 --> 00:08:58,700
Alright.

168
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:00,879
Xiaowei.

169
00:09:01,779 --> 00:09:03,019
Xiaowei, come down and eat.

170
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:05,100
You silly boy.

171
00:09:05,139 --> 00:09:05,960
Whatever's going on,

172
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:07,419
you gotta finish eating first.

173
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:08,200
Come down now.

174
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:09,519
Why are you calling him?

175
00:09:10,279 --> 00:09:11,080
Eat or don't, his choice.

176
00:09:11,539 --> 00:09:12,279
You're spoiling him rotten.

177
00:09:25,519 --> 00:09:26,679
You only know how to bully Xiaowei.

178
00:09:26,919 --> 00:09:28,179
Look at the Yang family across the way.

179
00:09:28,620 --> 00:09:30,240
A whole bunch of troublemakers are back.

180
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:32,539
Today they came to our door.

181
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:33,340
Tomorrow, who knows

182
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,159
what kind of trouble they'll stir up.

183
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,279
Things are gonna get lively now.

184
00:09:36,659 --> 00:09:37,340
With Xiaofang shouting like that

185
00:09:37,340 --> 00:09:38,279
up on the mountain,

186
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:40,720
Xiaowei's now a celebrity in our village.

187
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:41,840
So embarrassing.

188
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,639
My classmates are all saying

189
00:09:42,639 --> 00:09:44,159
my uncle got someone pregnant unmarried.

190
00:09:45,539 --> 00:09:46,940
Yang Fanhu's already done time once.

191
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,720
Does he want to go in a second time?

192
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:49,980
Let him make a fuss.

193
00:09:50,259 --> 00:09:51,259
Let's see how far he takes it.

194
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,980
Fuss, fuss, fuss!

195
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:54,840
If this keeps up, how can I marry Xiaofang?

196
00:09:55,360 --> 00:09:56,899
Why are you rushing to get married?

197
00:09:57,539 --> 00:09:58,940
Being pregnant before marriage is a good thing.

198
00:10:00,159 --> 00:10:01,379
The baby's in Yang Xiaofang's belly.

199
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:02,179
The ones who should be worried

200
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:03,360
are the Yangs.

201
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,740
Then am I even a man?

202
00:10:05,580 --> 00:10:06,340
I want to marry Xiaofang.

203
00:10:06,639 --> 00:10:07,679
And I need to give her a bride price.

204
00:10:08,220 --> 00:10:08,899
Bride price?

205
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,580
Do you know how much it costs

206
00:10:10,580 --> 00:10:11,419
to marry a wife these days?

207
00:10:11,779 --> 00:10:12,779
How much could it possibly cost?

208
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,440
You don't know anything

209
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,820
yet you dared to get a girl pregnant.

210
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:18,820
Getting a wife these days,

211
00:10:18,820 --> 00:10:19,980
there's no telling how much it takes.

212
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,600
You need a car and a house.

213
00:10:21,940 --> 00:10:23,580
Not like when your brother and I married.

214
00:10:23,919 --> 00:10:25,100
If I'd known, I would've married later.

215
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,879
Enough.

216
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:28,100
Have I shortchanged you?

217
00:10:28,279 --> 00:10:28,639
So what,

218
00:10:28,639 --> 00:10:30,039
you won't chip in a single cent?

219
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:32,659
I mean, when my brother got married,

220
00:10:32,659 --> 00:10:34,299
you bought him a house and a car.

221
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:36,100
You forked over the cash so willingly then.

222
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,860
Why is it so hard when it comes to me?

223
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:39,419
I'm asking for money for the sake of

224
00:10:39,419 --> 00:10:41,039
my future life with Xiaofang.

225
00:10:41,179 --> 00:10:42,340
What's wrong with supporting me a bit?

226
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:43,720
This cured meat

227
00:10:44,299 --> 00:10:45,360
was sent by your brother.

228
00:10:45,799 --> 00:10:46,679
The house renovation

229
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,080
was paid for by your brother.

230
00:10:48,940 --> 00:10:49,860
When your brother married his wife,

231
00:10:50,299 --> 00:10:51,440
you know what her family does?

232
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:52,899
They're contractors, aren't they?

233
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:54,279
Contractors.

234
00:10:55,200 --> 00:10:56,559
Your brother's house in the county

235
00:10:56,580 --> 00:10:57,480
was bought at insider price.

236
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,879
Do you know how much he saved?

237
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:01,259
He works construction with her dad.

238
00:11:01,299 --> 00:11:02,480
Do you know how much he makes?

239
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,059
The little bit you earn,

240
00:11:04,059 --> 00:11:04,940
no matter how much money I give you,

241
00:11:04,940 --> 00:11:06,399
it won't be enough after you're married.

242
00:11:07,580 --> 00:11:08,480
And you complain that I haven't lost

243
00:11:08,519 --> 00:11:09,600
enough money on you already?

244
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:13,019
Fine, I'm a money-loser.

245
00:11:14,240 --> 00:11:15,679
If I can't get married, just say so.

246
00:11:28,899 --> 00:11:29,700
Son

247
00:11:29,980 --> 00:11:31,080
Don't get worked up

248
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,659
Xiaofang's belly is huge now

249
00:11:34,019 --> 00:11:35,340
Who else would take her?

250
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,039
Right now

251
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:38,700
they're begging us

252
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:40,159
not the other way around

253
00:11:41,539 --> 00:11:42,980
No, how can I not worry?

254
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:45,039
The baby's about to be born

255
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:45,980
And you two, every single day

256
00:11:45,980 --> 00:11:47,700
it's money, money, money

257
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:49,299
What's that supposed to mean?

258
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:51,919
Shut your mouth

259
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,679
You can't even feed yourself

260
00:11:56,340 --> 00:11:56,799
Getting a wife

261
00:11:57,039 --> 00:11:58,159
I've gotta pay for it, right?

262
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,220
I've gotta raise your kid too, right?

263
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,559
Shut up and let me handle this

264
00:12:03,080 --> 00:12:03,899
It's a losing deal

265
00:12:04,159 --> 00:12:04,740
Just drag it out

266
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:05,919
The longer we stall

267
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,039
the cheaper it gets

268
00:12:08,919 --> 00:12:10,419
It's not Yang Xiaofang you look down on

269
00:12:10,860 --> 00:12:11,899
It's me you look down on, you...

270
00:12:12,820 --> 00:12:13,940
What kind of attitude is that?

271
00:12:14,139 --> 00:12:15,159
Like I owe you something

272
00:12:16,419 --> 00:12:17,659
Useless piece of trash

273
00:12:22,539 --> 00:12:23,840
Xiaofang's really got some nerve

274
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,639
Pregnant before marriage

275
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:26,940
and not even hiding it

276
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,100
Shouting it all over the hills

277
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,340
When did she and the Qi's second son

278
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,340
even hook up?

279
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,500
And so fast, she already

280
00:12:31,500 --> 00:12:32,340
got knocked up

281
00:12:32,340 --> 00:12:33,519
I saw it with my own eyes today

282
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,600
The whole Yang family came back

283
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,820
And cornered that kid

284
00:12:37,100 --> 00:12:38,740
on the field ridge, beat him good

285
00:12:38,879 --> 00:12:40,139
