I swear, you're

577
00:26:16,460 --> 00:26:17,640
such a chameleon

578
00:26:23,700 --> 00:26:24,339
Auntie

579
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:26,180
Little Auntie

580
00:26:26,660 --> 00:26:27,299
As for me

581
00:26:27,420 --> 00:26:29,220
I'm different from Auntie back then

582
00:26:29,460 --> 00:26:30,960
Because I have you guys

583
00:26:31,220 --> 00:26:31,960
I have you all

584
00:26:32,660 --> 00:26:34,819
So I have both courage and luck

585
00:26:35,539 --> 00:26:36,519
That's why I'm not afraid of anything

586
00:26:59,819 --> 00:27:01,180
I brought you guys presents!

587
00:27:02,259 --> 00:27:03,420
Presents? What kind?

588
00:27:03,539 --> 00:27:04,200
What is this?

589
00:27:05,079 --> 00:27:05,700
Which one's mine?

590
00:27:08,220 --> 00:27:09,299
Deer antlers.

591
00:27:09,960 --> 00:27:10,819
Horse face.

592
00:27:11,400 --> 00:27:12,380
Cow's body, I guess.

593
00:27:12,819 --> 00:27:13,140
And this...

594
00:27:13,460 --> 00:27:14,140
A donkey's tail.

595
00:27:15,460 --> 00:27:17,039
Why are its eyes rolled up like that?

596
00:27:18,019 --> 00:27:18,640
It's a total mishmash.

597
00:27:19,180 --> 00:27:19,819
Doesn't it look like you?

598
00:27:21,940 --> 00:27:23,039
I look like a mishmash?

599
00:27:24,079 --> 00:27:24,940
Are you praising me

600
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:25,779
or insulting me?

601
00:27:26,079 --> 00:27:26,819
This is a peacock, right?

602
00:27:27,299 --> 00:27:28,319
Think it looks like you?

603
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,619
This peacock is just like me.

604
00:27:29,759 --> 00:27:31,380
At least it's better than a mishmash.

605
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,460
Looks like anything but yourself.

606
00:27:32,460 --> 00:27:33,619
You're clearly just a pheasant

607
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,279
with peacock feathers stuck in.

608
00:27:34,279 --> 00:27:35,680
How am I a pheasant?

609
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:38,700
In Xiaofang's eyes, I'm a peacock.

610
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:39,960
Right?

611
00:27:39,960 --> 00:27:40,720
Show me you can fly then.

612
00:27:40,759 --> 00:27:41,579
Watch me fly!

613
00:27:45,339 --> 00:27:45,859
Fanyan.

614
00:27:46,160 --> 00:27:47,759
Why can't you just understand me a little?

615
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,019
You're this old already,

616
00:27:49,240 --> 00:27:50,240
and still so stubborn?

617
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:55,440
Hurry up and cut it!

618
00:28:55,519 --> 00:28:56,660
Before he wakes up!

619
00:28:59,380 --> 00:29:00,140
Xiaofang!

620
00:29:01,339 --> 00:29:02,180
Cut it, quick!

621
00:29:02,539 --> 00:29:03,359
He's gonna wake up soon.

622
00:29:04,119 --> 00:29:04,880
How am I supposed to cut it?

623
00:29:05,019 --> 00:29:05,460
Help me out!

624
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:06,660
Over here, over here!

625
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:07,579
Here, here, here!

626
00:29:07,859 --> 00:29:08,240
Yes!

627
00:29:19,640 --> 00:29:20,240
Hey, what are you doing?

628
00:29:20,359 --> 00:29:20,960
What do you think I'm doing?

629
00:29:24,559 --> 00:29:25,480
I said I'm not cutting it!

630
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:26,700
What are you yelling for?

631
00:29:27,099 --> 00:29:28,240
You're getting married, becoming a dad!

632
00:29:28,599 --> 00:29:29,740
You don't listen to me anymore, huh?

633
00:29:30,099 --> 00:29:32,000
Getting married and shaving my head

634
00:29:32,119 --> 00:29:32,960
are two different things!

635
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:38,819
Dad,

636
00:29:39,619 --> 00:29:40,460
so you mean

637
00:29:40,599 --> 00:29:42,640
you agree to let me marry Xiaofang

638
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,839
and give me the bride price money?

639
00:29:45,980 --> 00:29:47,339
I say one thing, you say another.

640
00:29:47,579 --> 00:29:49,099
You're way off the topic!

641
00:29:54,160 --> 00:29:54,740
What are you trying to do?

642
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:55,900
I'll compromise once more.

643
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:57,099
You give me that money,

644
00:29:57,119 --> 00:29:58,180
and I'll shave my head.

645
00:29:58,259 --> 00:29:58,980
Bull!

646
00:29:59,319 --> 00:30:00,680
Is your hair made of gold?

647
00:30:00,680 --> 00:30:01,599
That valuable, huh?

648
00:30:01,980 --> 00:30:02,619
Shave it or don't.

649
00:30:02,819 --> 00:30:03,700
See how people will laugh at you.

650
00:30:04,279 --> 00:30:05,619
All I want is fairness here.

651
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:07,039
Just give me what's owed to me.

652
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,440
Besides, Xiaofang already said

653
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,839
she's marrying me, not the bride price.

654
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:11,339
You...

655
00:30:11,920 --> 00:30:13,200
You believe what she says?

656
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,299
If you don't give it to her,

657
00:30:14,500 --> 00:30:15,579
see if she still marries you!

658
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:16,819
You don't understand her.

659
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:18,099
Oh, we don't understand, huh?

660
00:30:18,099 --> 00:30:18,779
And you do?

661
00:30:19,200 --> 00:30:19,500
Fine.

662
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,940
Let me show you how well you know her.

663
00:30:22,660 --> 00:30:23,099
Password.

664
00:30:24,079 --> 00:30:24,779
That's private!

665
00:30:25,259 --> 00:30:25,859
Password!

666
00:30:25,980 --> 00:30:28,400
Password, password, give it!

667
00:30:28,980 --> 00:30:29,319
Say it!

668
00:30:29,339 --> 00:30:29,720
Say it!

669
00:30:32,279 --> 00:30:32,799
1314.

670
00:30:34,180 --> 00:30:35,180
1314?

671
00:30:35,220 --> 00:30:35,759
1314.

672
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:38,920
So my son's a real romantic.

673
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:40,819
Romantic my foot! "Forever and ever"?

674
00:30:41,079 --> 00:30:42,519
You're ruining your dad forever and ever!

675
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,420
This is just for engagement.

676
00:30:47,640 --> 00:30:49,019
For the wedding, it won't be this one.

677
00:30:49,299 --> 00:30:49,799
For the wedding,

678
00:30:49,799 --> 00:30:50,720
I'll get a big diamond ring.

679
00:30:50,880 --> 00:30:52,319
A big diamond ring too?

680
00:30:53,180 --> 00:30:53,700
Xiaofang,

681
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:55,920
didn't you say you're getting married?

682
00:30:56,200 --> 00:30:57,059
Have you discussed the bride price?

683
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,240
Talked about it ages ago.

684
00:30:59,240 --> 00:30:59,680
Yeah, we talked.

685
00:31:00,079 --> 00:31:00,559
We talked.

686
00:31:01,839 --> 00:31:02,240
How much?

687
00:31:02,859 --> 00:31:03,319
Doesn't matter.

688
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:04,920
Doesn't matter?

689
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:07,180
How can it not matter?

690
00:31:07,559 --> 00:31:09,519
In the countryside now, men outnumber women.

691
00:31:09,519 --> 00:31:11,920
Requirements have doubled since years ago.

692
00:31:13,579 --> 00:31:15,039
So how much bride price did you get?

693
00:31:16,319 --> 00:31:16,940
It's a secret.

694
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,599
Fine, forget it then.

695
00:31:20,259 --> 00:31:23,259
Xiaofang, I miss you.

696
00:31:24,519 --> 00:31:27,599
Dad's asking your family's bride price.

697
00:31:28,539 --> 00:31:29,059
Hehe.

698
00:31:39,940 --> 00:31:41,880
What are you laughing at?

699
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:44,059
He's asking about the bride price.

700
00:31:44,599 --> 00:31:45,759
Qi Xiaowei's not bad!

701
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,140
He convinced his dad already?

702
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:49,960
Reply for me.

703
00:31:50,380 --> 00:31:51,359
My hands are covered in herbs.

704
00:31:51,579 --> 00:31:52,160
Just tell him,

705
00:31:52,559 --> 00:31:53,420
whatever bride price is fine.

706
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:54,079
I don't care.

707
00:31:54,259 --> 00:31:55,900
Don't care, don't care...

708
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:56,920
Wait, Xiaofang.

709
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:58,059
This kind of thing,

710
00:31:58,059 --> 00:31:59,579
how can you not care?

711
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:01,140
You can't be careless about this!

712
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:05,099
Ask too little and they'll look down on us.

713
00:32:05,200 --> 00:32:06,740
They'll think you're desperate for him.

714
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,480
Exactly.

715
00:32:08,279 --> 00:32:09,559
Let me think how to reply.

716
00:32:12,819 --> 00:32:15,039
A car and a house.

717
00:32:18,299 --> 00:32:18,880
Sent.

718
00:32:19,039 --> 00:32:19,440
Take a look.

719
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:21,680
Oh my god.

720
00:32:22,279 --> 00:32:22,880
What does that mean?

721
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:23,819
What does it mean?

722
00:32:24,059 --> 00:32:25,420
"Moving" means a car.

723
00:32:25,579 --> 00:32:27,299
"Not moving" means real estate, a house.

724
00:32:27,420 --> 00:32:29,680
So she wants a house and a car.

725
00:32:31,599 --> 00:32:32,660
You call this knowing her?

726
00:32:33,960 --> 00:32:35,400
You call this not caring about bride price?

727
00:32:36,539 --> 00:32:37,640
But isn't that just how it should be?

728
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:38,599
As a man,

729
00:32:38,599 --> 00:32:39,420
shouldn't I provide these?

730
00:32:39,799 --> 00:32:40,420
Besides,

731
00:32:40,420 --> 00:32:41,940
Xiaofang's not asking for a mansion

732
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:42,920
or a luxury car.

733
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:44,519
Look carefully.

734
00:32:44,559 --> 00:32:46,140
There's also "Shake off the in-laws, help out your family."

735
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,420
"Shake off" means shake off trouble.

736
00:32:48,799 --> 00:32:49,740
Start a separate household.

737
00:32:50,099 --> 00:32:52,200
Absolutely no living with the in-laws.

738
00:32:52,400 --> 00:32:54,079
Marriage nowadays has so many rules.

739
00:32:54,240 --> 00:32:55,519
And "help out"

740
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:56,740
means helping her own family.

741
00:32:56,900 --> 00:32:57,799
The bride price money

742
00:32:57,839 --> 00:32:58,940
must stay with her family.

743
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,039
Holiday and birthday gifts,

744
00:33:00,140 --> 00:33:01,079
gifts are a must.

745
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,220
Isn't bride price discouraged these days?

746
00:33:03,519 --> 00:33:04,759
Sure, having it is nice,

747
00:33:04,839 --> 00:33:06,619
but not having it isn't the end of the world.

748
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:07,500
How can that be okay?

749
00:33:07,859 --> 00:33:08,799
She's not even married in yet,

750
00:33:08,799 --> 00:33:10,140
and she's already trying to shake us off.

751
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,099
Just trying to funnel money to her family.

752
00:33:13,700 --> 00:33:14,740
You and Xiaofang used to be

753
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:15,819
childhood sweethearts, sure.

754
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:16,819
But look at now.

755
00:33:17,599 --> 00:33:19,279
A road separates the two families.

756
00:33:19,400 --> 00:33:20,680
People have changed long ago.

757
00:33:21,059 --> 00:33:22,380
And you're still stuck on "one, three, one, four."

758
00:33:22,380 --> 00:33:23,779
I say you're a total idiot.

759
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:25,480
Xiaofang didn't send this.

760
00:33:25,480 --> 00:33:25,940
I'll go ask her.

761
00:33:26,119 --> 00:33:26,539
Come back!

762
00:33:27,079 --> 00:33:27,599
Right now,

763
00:33:27,880 --> 00:33:28,339
you can't go.

764
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,160
The tenser it gets, the calmer you stay.

765
00:33:30,339 --> 00:33:31,380
You idiot!

766
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,359
What is there to ask?

767
00:33:32,559 --> 00:33:33,299
Xiaofang is just

768
00:33:33,299 --> 00:33:34,240
sweet-talking you.

769
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,200
Son,

770
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,660
you've been fooled.

771
00:33:37,539 --> 00:33:38,960
You've been brainless since childhood.

772
00:33:39,180 --> 00:33:41,000
How'd you get even worse as an adult?

773
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:43,500
You've disgraced the entire Qi family!

774
00:33:43,799 --> 00:33:44,359
Do you know what you

775
00:33:44,359 --> 00:33:45,240
look like right now?

776
00:33:45,980 --> 00:33:46,819
You look just like

777
00:33:47,259 --> 00:33:48,819
a bitter woman cheated of money and love.

778
00:33:48,819 --> 00:33:49,759
A bitter woman, you get it?

779
00:33:49,759 --> 00:33:50,259
Bitter!

780
00:33:52,279 --> 00:33:52,660
You...

781
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:56,200
Son, you...

782
00:33:56,319 --> 00:33:57,660
Don't do anything stupid!

783
00:34:20,639 --> 00:34:21,159
Xiaowei

784
00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:22,940
Don't run, slow down

785
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:25,239
I came as soon as I got your message

786
00:34:26,119 --> 00:34:26,920
Still, you shouldn't run

787
00:34:27,039 --> 00:34:28,079
Look how big your belly is

788
00:34:28,159 --> 00:34:29,159
What if you fall?

789
00:34:29,780 --> 00:34:30,360
I won't

790
00:34:30,360 --> 00:34:31,739
I've been running here since I was a kid

791
00:34:32,960 --> 00:34:33,400
Look

792
00:34:34,460 --> 00:34:35,400
If you step on this

793
00:34:35,860 --> 00:34:36,659
you'll definitely fall

794
00:34:36,980 --> 00:34:38,460
You're going to be a mom

795
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:40,099
Can't you act like one?

796
00:34:40,219 --> 00:34:41,619
I'm not a mom yet, am I?

797
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:42,760
What are you doing?

798
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:44,679
Wait

799
00:34:45,840 --> 00:34:46,400
Xiaowei

800
00:34:48,000 --> 00:34:49,059
You cut your hair

801
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:49,960
Let me see

802
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:52,599
Let me have a look

803
00:34:53,360 --> 00:34:54,400
Who cut it for you?

804
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:55,659
My dad

805
00:34:57,699 --> 00:34:59,039
He told you to cut it and you just did?

806
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:00,659
You looked so handsome with long hair

807
00:35:04,519 --> 00:35:05,760
Yang Xiaofang, you've changed

808
00:35:08,099 --> 00:35:08,760
Now spill it

809
00:35:09,420 --> 00:35:10,860
That "A car and a house"

810
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:11,980
"Shake off the in-laws, help out your family"

811
00:35:12,019 --> 00:35:12,579
What's that about?

812
00:35:13,739 --> 00:35:15,260
Those are new terms I just learned today

813
00:35:15,719 --> 00:35:16,559
Let me tell you, getting married nowadays

814
00:35:16,559 --> 00:35:17,579
is really terrifying

815
00:35:18,119 --> 00:35:19,639
"A car and a house" means

816
00:35:19,679 --> 00:35:20,860
a house and a car

817
00:35:20,860 --> 00:35:22,400
And "Shake off the in-laws, help out your family" means

818
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:22,719
you have to...

819
00:35:22,860 --> 00:35:23,860
So you really posted it?

820
00:35:24,780 --> 00:35:25,860
Of course I didn't post it

821
00:35:26,019 --> 00:35:27,659
Xiao Zhu and Xiao Chao posted it as a joke

822
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:28,699
Wait

823
00:35:28,699 --> 00:35:30,199
How could you let them mess around like that?

824
00:35:30,360 --> 00:35:31,920
Now my dad and everyone got the wrong idea

825
00:35:32,099 --> 00:35:33,280
They think you'll jack up the price.

826
00:35:34,579 --> 00:35:36,119
What about you? Do you think that?

827
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,000
Of course that's not what I think

828
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:39,539
Then we're fine

829
00:35:40,159 --> 00:35:40,719
As for the bride price

830
00:35:40,739 --> 00:35:41,719
haven't we already discussed it?

831
00:35:49,199 --> 00:35:49,760
Don't worry.

832
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:50,980
About the bride price,

833
00:35:51,039 --> 00:35:52,440
I'll definitely fight for you all the way.

834
00:35:53,599 --> 00:35:54,139
You're silly.

835
00:35:54,579 --> 00:35:55,460
The sun's behind you.

836
00:35:57,280 --> 00:35:58,079
Right. Here.

837
00:35:59,880 --> 00:36:01,280
My goose just laid this egg.

838
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,280
I snuck it out for you.

839
00:36:02,420 --> 00:36:03,199
When I left the house,

840
00:36:03,199 --> 00:36:04,300
it followed me the whole way.

841
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:07,019
The egg's already been boiled.

842
00:36:07,039 --> 00:36:07,960
And it still followed you?

843
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,460
Okay, I may have

844
00:36:10,460 --> 00:36:11,159
added a little bit of

845
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:12,239
artistic embellishment.

846
00:36:12,599 --> 00:36:13,860
But this goose egg is real,

847
00:36:14,480 --> 00:36:16,300
And my heart for Yang Xiaofang is real too.

848
00:36:21,420 --> 00:36:23,639
But you look bad with your long hair cut.

849
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:25,119
Your face is so round,

850
00:36:25,500 --> 00:36:26,260
you'll look like a braised egg.

851
00:36:30,219 --> 00:36:31,519
If he cuts his, I'll grow mine out.

852
00:36:32,139 --> 00:36:33,400
Just wait. In a year,

853
00:36:33,519 --> 00:36:34,940
I'll still be that handsome fuzzy-headed guy.

854
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:37,840
Well said.

855
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:39,460
As long as we don't change,

856
00:36:39,460 --> 00:36:40,760
nothing can change us.

857
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:42,239
Let's go.

858
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:43,780
Braised egg.

859
00:36:44,679 --> 00:36:45,260
Braised egg.

860
00:36:45,579 --> 00:36:46,820
Braised egg, braised egg.

861
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,639
Maybe the villagers

862
00:36:48,699 --> 00:36:51,019
don't understand what Xiaowei and I have.

863
00:36:51,719 --> 00:36:52,820
But actually,

864
00:36:52,820 --> 00:36:54,139
what they don't know is,

865
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:55,500
when I was ten years old...

866
00:36:55,500 --> 00:36:56,039
Xiaofang.

867
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:58,059
That was the year I endured

868
00:36:58,119 --> 00:36:59,320
the most gossip and rumors.

869
00:36:59,739 --> 00:37:01,880
Xiaowei was the only one who held my hand.

870
00:37:02,860 --> 00:37:03,719
I bought you a popsicle.

871
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:04,920
I don't want it.

872
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:07,940
I've arranged everything.

873
00:37:08,159 --> 00:37:09,420
I came back this time to take you with me.

874
00:37:09,719 --> 00:37:10,099
Okay?

875
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:10,980
Come with Mommy.

876
00:37:11,559 --> 00:37:11,880
Let's go.

877
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:13,539
No, I don't need you to care about me.

878
00:37:13,840 --> 00:37:15,280
What are you doing, Xiaofang?

879
00:37:15,480 --> 00:37:16,699
Your dad's been locked up.

880
00:37:17,039 --> 00:37:17,619
If I don't take care of you, who will?

881
00:37:17,619 --> 00:37:18,360
I said, I don't need you to take care of me!

882
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:19,159
I don't need you!

883
00:37:19,539 --> 00:37:21,300
If you leave with him, don't come back!

884
00:37:21,460 --> 00:37:23,059
Her dad's been locked up, I heard.

885
00:37:24,300 --> 00:37:25,860
Is that her mom coming to get her?

886
00:37:26,719 --> 00:37:28,260
How can she treat her mom like that?

887
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:29,320
What business is it of yours?

888
00:37:29,739 --> 00:37:30,659
Mind your own business!

889
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,260
Xiaofang, let's go.

890
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:39,960
Xiaofang!

891
00:37:41,079 --> 00:37:41,699
Xiaofang!

892
00:37:43,119 --> 00:37:43,880
Xiaofang!

893
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:56,059
The village gossip

894
00:37:56,079 --> 00:37:57,519
is like the mountain wind.

895
00:37:58,340 --> 00:38:01,139
From the east today, smelling of dirt.

896
00:38:02,119 --> 00:38:04,320
Tomorrow it drifts west and is gone.

897
00:38:05,519 --> 00:38:07,280
I never care what others say.

898
00:38:07,880 --> 00:38:09,400
I just want to hold on to what's in my heart,

899
00:38:09,440 --> 00:38:11,579
this steadiness and sincerity.

900
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,260
Let me tell you guys

901
00:38:41,659 --> 00:38:42,880
When Xiaofang and I were kids

902
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:43,920
the elders in the village said

903
00:38:44,519 --> 00:38:46,019
if you catch a firefly

904
00:38:46,019 --> 00:38:47,159
you get to make a wish

905
00:38:47,719 --> 00:38:48,980
My biggest wish right now

906
00:38:49,340 --> 00:38:50,739
is that my wedding with Xiaofang

907
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:51,900
goes off without a hitch

908
00:38:52,420 --> 00:38:53,320
I mean, come on

909
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:54,619
You said it yourself before

910
00:38:54,699 --> 00:38:56,760
"I'll never marry or have kids early"

911
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:57,860
And look at you

912
00:38:58,139 --> 00:38:59,400
Out of all of us, you're pretty much

913
00:38:59,400 --> 00:39:00,440
the first one to make it out there

914
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:01,619
Are you really okay

915
00:39:01,619 --> 00:39:02,719
getting reeled in by Yang Xiaofang?

916
00:39:05,539 --> 00:39:06,300
Yeah, I'm good with it

917
00:39:09,199 --> 00:39:10,519
I came back just to

918
00:39:10,880 --> 00:39:11,820
get married, have a kid

919
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,760
And in a few months

920
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:13,420
I'm heading back out

921
00:39:13,599 --> 00:39:14,179
But

922
00:39:14,639 --> 00:39:16,739
people in this village are so nosy

923
00:39:17,099 --> 00:39:17,780
Behind your back

924
00:39:18,039 --> 00:39:18,940
they're always pointing fingers

925
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,219
No sense of boundaries at all

926
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:21,480
Well, you know how it is

927
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,320
in a village like ours

928
00:39:22,579 --> 00:39:23,699
With all the aunties and uncles

929
00:39:23,699 --> 00:39:25,059
everyone's related somehow

930
00:39:25,639 --> 00:39:26,320
That thing you mentioned

931
00:39:26,320 --> 00:39:27,320
that sense of whatever

932
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,860
that's a city folk thing

933
00:39:28,900 --> 00:39:30,059
In our village, that doesn't exist

934
00:39:30,559 --> 00:39:31,980
Bro, let me be straight with you

935
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:33,539
You gotta get Xiaofang

936
00:39:33,539 --> 00:39:34,500
to change that personality of hers

937
00:39:34,940 --> 00:39:35,880
What's wrong with Xiaofang's personality?

938
00:39:37,280 --> 00:39:38,219
Why should she change?

939
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:39,139
She's free-spirited

940
00:39:39,139 --> 00:39:40,059
does whatever she wants

941
00:39:40,539 --> 00:39:41,659
That's exactly what I love about her

942
00:39:42,900 --> 00:39:43,519
So her shouting up on the mountain

943
00:39:43,519 --> 00:39:44,340
announcing she's pregnant

944
00:39:44,340 --> 00:39:45,719
you don't mind that at all?

945
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:46,820
Give it a rest

946
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,539
She's gonna be a mom

947
00:39:56,619 --> 00:39:57,880
She should be happy, right?

948
00:40:02,639 --> 00:40:03,599
But honestly

949
00:40:05,199 --> 00:40:06,159
this whole thing

950
00:40:06,539 --> 00:40:07,900
did come a bit too suddenly

951
00:40:09,159 --> 00:40:10,559
We haven't even dated that long

952
00:40:11,059 --> 00:40:12,079
and suddenly I'm a dad

953
00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:15,699
But she's already pregnant

954
00:40:15,699 --> 00:40:16,980
I've gotta take responsibility, right?

955
00:40:18,360 --> 00:40:18,699
Oh, by the way

956
00:40:19,099 --> 00:40:20,440
Doesn't your brother work

957
00:40:20,719 --> 00:40:22,380
at the county cultural center?

958
00:40:23,219 --> 00:40:24,800
I wanna hold an art exhibition

959
00:40:25,199 --> 00:40:25,760
A what now?

960
00:40:25,920 --> 00:40:26,559
An art exhibition

961
00:40:26,639 --> 00:40:27,739
Sell paintings, make money

962
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,159
I gotta support myself

963
00:40:29,639 --> 00:40:30,539
We've gotta help you out

964
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,380
That's what bros are for

965
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:34,480
Take a look at these

966
00:40:38,000 --> 00:40:38,719
I painted them all

967
00:40:39,940 --> 00:40:40,559
They can be sold

968
00:40:42,179 --> 00:40:43,199
Should've picked up painting myself

969
00:40:45,119 --> 00:40:46,739
You've done quite a lot here

970
00:40:47,139 --> 00:40:47,860
Not bad at all

971
00:40:48,320 --> 00:40:49,619
Looks like you can make good money

972
00:41:04,280 --> 00:41:04,780
Wait, wait

973
00:41:06,059 --> 00:41:07,219
Who's this naked one?

974
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:08,679
Who is she?

975
00:41:10,940 --> 00:41:11,639
Xiaofang, obviously

976
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:13,280
That's Yang Xiaofang

977
00:41:13,579 --> 00:41:14,400
Who else could it be?

978
00:41:14,539 --> 00:41:15,300
Other than her

979
00:41:15,300 --> 00:41:16,980
who'd strip down and let you paint them?

980
00:41:26,239 --> 00:41:27,360
Why did you send it out?

981
00:41:28,519 --> 00:41:29,780
Stop sharing it! Recall it, now!

982
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:30,340
Just sharing, sharing

983
00:41:47,219 --> 00:41:48,239
Such strong wind

984
00:42:10,800 --> 00:42:11,800
The wind's picking up.

985
00:42:14,159 --> 00:42:15,519
Weather's about to turn.

986
00:42:27,340 --> 00:42:27,719
Xiao Lin!

987
00:42:28,519 --> 00:42:28,900
Xiao Lin!

988
00:42:29,679 --> 00:42:30,000
Hurry!

989
00:42:32,719 --> 00:42:33,400
Who's this?

990
00:42:33,619 --> 00:42:34,019
Yeah, right?

991
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,400
Looks like Yang Xiaofang.

992
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,820
Who'd do something so shameless?

993
00:42:40,199 --> 00:42:41,940
These young folks sure have guts.

994
00:42:42,019 --> 00:42:43,000
So wild these days!

995
00:42:43,260 --> 00:42:44,000
What do you know?

996
00:42:44,079 --> 00:42:44,719
It's called being open-minded.

997
00:42:45,860 --> 00:42:46,960
Open-minded, my foot!

998
00:42:46,960 --> 00:42:48,179
She's stripped bare!

999
00:42:48,619 --> 00:42:49,659
They're young, you know?

1000
00:42:49,679 --> 00:42:50,500
They live wild.

1001
00:42:51,019 --> 00:42:52,039
What decent girl would

1002
00:42:52,039 --> 00:42:53,280
strip naked to be painted?

1003
00:42:54,539 --> 00:42:56,099
I don't think Yang Xiaofang

1004
00:42:56,119 --> 00:42:57,159
can stay in this village anymore.

1005
00:42:57,900 --> 00:42:58,760
How could she do that?

1006
00:43:23,380 --> 00:43:25,320
This is Xiaofang's own business.

1007
00:43:25,679 --> 00:43:26,980
But you bunch of grown-ups

1008
00:43:26,980 --> 00:43:28,099
had to butt in.

1009
00:43:28,519 --> 00:43:29,960
A perfectly good relationship,

1010
00:43:30,260 --> 00:43:32,219
and you all ruined it.

1011
00:43:32,219 --> 00:43:33,579
Why do I feel like ever since you got back,

1012
00:43:33,579 --> 00:43:34,739
you're like a completely different person?

1013
00:43:35,480 --> 00:43:37,260
This isn't just between you and Qi Xiaowei

1014
00:43:37,340 --> 00:43:38,420
as two people anymore.

1015
00:43:38,679 --> 00:43:41,039
This is now a war between two families.

1016
00:43:41,079 --> 00:43:41,780
What... what are you doing?

1017
00:43:42,940 --> 00:43:43,599
Yang Fanmei!

1018
00:43:43,760 --> 00:43:44,980
You dare throw a shoe at me?

1019
00:43:45,280 --> 00:43:46,239
We want to report a case.

1020
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:47,099
A homicide case.

1021
00:43:48,840 --> 00:43:49,280
Old Qi!

1022
00:43:49,400 --> 00:43:51,460
The Yangs filed charges against Xiaowei!

1023
00:43:51,719 --> 00:43:52,820
Charges... against me?
